These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, scientific
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, british
2 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, subway
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice       | iced-tea    |
| Job           | mechanic | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | comedy   |
| Nationality   | british  | argentine     |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | cat     |
| Transport     | helicopter     | subway        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, fishing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, disaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, rock
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, boat
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the fan of rock##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea        | sprite   |
| Hobby         | fishing | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | rock     |
| Pet           | cat        | chinchilla    |
| Transport     | bus  | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
