The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, dutch
2 different pets are kept: horse, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, sailing
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | spinach    | apricot      |
| Hobby         | collecting   | dancing       |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | drama |
| Nationality   | dutch  | chinese    |
| Pet           | horse       | snake   |
| Sport         | sailing   | rowing     |

